Package lazyTrees

Class LazySearchTree<E extends Comparable<? super E>>

java.lang.Object
lazyTrees.LazySearchTree<E>
public class LazySearchTree<E extends Comparable<? super E>> extends Object
A binary search tree with lazy deletion functionality tracks the size of the tree both hard (all nodes) and soft (non deleted nodes)
Author:
Foothill College, Jason Palmeri

    a Private class to LazySearchTree that creates a Node object for each Object in the binary search tree keeps track of the left and right children, data and if the node is lazily deleted
